{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The only thing was very cold because the place that I have-- there was no place where to heat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I would stay, you know, at night, I would stay with this, this Jewish couple till I went to bed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in bed was OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I was constantly worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I said to myself, here I am in bed, and it's-- you know, I have a cover, and I have a blanket.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And God only knows if my-- you know, I knew my father was dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But my mother, and my sister, and my brother, what-- and if they have anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's going on with them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they can work that hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they could do-- because we used to get up five o'clock in the morning and go to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And come home in the dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they can do all these things, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was constantly on my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just had no peace of mind because constantly was-- this in my thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, in the meantime, you know, let's say, you just lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And There was organizations in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You made friends in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You, you-- you know, you, you had meetings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's all these things were going on, you know, in the ghetto if you really wanted to, to be involved.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I, I didn't have such a bad life in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, 1944, when they took everybody out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they took, like, portions, let's say, of this street, of this section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- the Jewish police would tell you, because I was in this, you know-- and where I worked, they had radio, that the underground, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would-- we would know exactly where the Russians are.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
